{"word":"G2551 - κακολογέω - kakologéō - kak-ol-og-eh'-o - Curse","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κακολογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kakologéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kak-ol-og-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Curse</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிந்தி, தீங்குசொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. to speak ill of, revile, abuse, one; to calumniate, traduce"},{"paragraph":"2. to imprecate evil on, curse"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a> nad <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>; to <i>revile:</i> - curse, speak evil of.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}